text: Canlubang Golf & Country Club, shortly known as Can Golf, is located in barrio Casile, Cabuyao, Laguna.https://cangolf.com.ph/about The history of the area was part of a large sugarcane plantation owned by Jos√© Yulo, a known politician and landowner in the mid-20th century. The club occupies part of this land, later transforming it into a golfing venue. ==Features== Canlubang Golf & Country Club features two 18-hole courses, these courses offer a total of 36 holes. It is one of the gold courses along with Santa Elena Golf Course in Cabuyao city. ==References== Category:Laguna (province)
